org.sxb.session

インタフェース ExpiringSession

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    Session
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    MapSession

    public interface ExpiringSession
extends Session
    A Session that contains additional attributes that are useful for determining if a session is expired.
    導入されたバージョン:
    1.0
    作成者:
    Jeffson

    • フィールドの概要

      • インタフェースから継承されたフィールド org.sxb.session.Session

        PRINCIPAL_NAME_ATTRIBUTE_NAME

    • メソッドの概要

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      Gets the time when this session was created in milliseconds since midnight of 1/1/1970 GMT.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • getCreationTime

        long getCreationTime()
        Gets the time when this session was created in milliseconds since midnight of 1/1/1970 GMT.
        戻り値:
        the time when this session was created in milliseconds since midnight of 1/1/1970 GMT.

      • getLastAccessedTime

        long getLastAccessedTime()
        Gets the last time this Session was accessed expressed in milliseconds since midnight of 1/1/1970 GMT
        戻り値:
        the last time the client sent a request associated with the session expressed in milliseconds since midnight of 1/1/1970 GMT

      • setMaxInactiveIntervalInSeconds

        void setMaxInactiveIntervalInSeconds(int interval)
        Sets the maximum inactive interval in seconds between requests before this session will be invalidated. A negative time indicates that the session will never timeout.
        パラメータ:
        interval - the number of seconds that the Session should be kept alive between client requests.

      • getMaxInactiveIntervalInSeconds

        int getMaxInactiveIntervalInSeconds()
        Gets the maximum inactive interval in seconds between requests before this session will be invalidated. A negative time indicates that the session will never timeout.
        戻り値:
        the maximum inactive interval in seconds between requests before this session will be invalidated. A negative time indicates that the session will never timeout.

      • isExpired

        boolean isExpired()
        Returns true if the session is expired.
        戻り値:
        true if the session is expired, else false.
